<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1816] Master rewrite</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1816</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;An umbrella issue for master rewrite.  Master rewrite is a new feature for 0.21 hbase.  I&apos;m attaching &quot;Master Rewrite&quot; notes taken at the SU SF hbase meetup made by JGray.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12434794">HBASE-1816</key>
            <summary>Master rewrite</summary>
